  "special": {
    "title": "A simple solution to a dire problem.",
    "description": "Always incendiary. Each trigger pull fires 10 shots arranged in two rows while consuming 6 ammo. It gains extra damage and magazine size, but loses fire rate and reload speed. While scoped, it still uses Dahl burst fire. With Mouthwash equipped it gains a major damage bonus, and in the Writhing Deep the Retainer also grants movement and jump bonuses while it is equipped."
  },
  "notes": "Its damage is boosted further while the Mouthwash relic is equipped. It only spawns with a Vladof sight. The spread pattern resembles the Pitchfork, with clustered projectile groups and extra ammo consumption per shot. A safer farm spot is near the Dahl Abandon exit to the Burrows, where the bandits are less dangerous than the infected deeper inside.",
